Details available at wiki: http://wiki.github.com/champjss/archiftp

=== Required bundles ===

==== Felix ====
* Apache Felix Log Service (1.0.0) (http://felix.apache.org/site/downloads.cgi)
* Apache Felix Metatype Service (1.0.2) (http://felix.apache.org/site/downloads.cgi)
* Apache Felix Configuration Admin Service (1.0.10) (http://felix.apache.org/site/downloads.cgi)
* HTTP Service (Jetty) (1.0.0) (http://felix.apache.org/site/downloads.cgi)

==== Springsouce ====
* OSGi Release 4.0.1 Services (3.1.200.v20071203) (http://www.springsource.com/repository/app/bundle/version/detail?name=org.eclipse.osgi.services&version=3.1.200.v20071203&searchType=bundlesByPackage&searchQuery=org.osgi.service.http)
* Java Servlet API (2.5.0) (http://www.springsource.com/repository/app/bundle/version/detail?name=com.springsource.javax.servlet&version=2.5.0&searchType=bundlesBySymbolicName&searchQuery=javax.servlet)

=== Additional bundles ===
* Apache Felix Web Management Console (1.2.8) (http://felix.apache.org/site/downloads.cgi)
* luminis Configuration Admin command line client (0.2.3) (https://opensource.luminis.net/wiki/display/SITE/OSGi+Configuration+Admin+command+line+client)

=== How to use ===
* access to logpage with url http://localhost:8080/archiftp/log
* access to configuration admin page with url http://localhost:8080/system/console (If Apache Felix Web Management Console is installed). Username and password is initialize as 'admin'.
